<p><strong>Sources</strong> <Link to="/source/npc_codex">NPC Codex pg. 150</Link><br/><strong>XP</strong> 9,600<br/>Elf <Link to="/class/rogue">rogue</Link> 11<br/>NE Medium humanoid (elf)<br/><strong>Init</strong> +5; <strong>Senses</strong> low-light vision; Perception +17</p>
